<lb n="1"/>svasti sakavarṣaṁbulu 1051 
<lb n="2"/>gu nāṁḍu yuttarāyaṇa 
<lb n="3"/>saṁkrāntinimittamuna <unclear>keṁdū</unclear>ri 
<lb n="4"/><unclear>cō</unclear>ḍamahārā jaina permmāḍi 
<lb n="5"/>dēvani [A]nuṁgu rēkamadēvi ko 
<lb n="6" break="no"/>mmūri yagastīśvaramahādēvaraku 
<lb n="7"/>Akhaṁḍavarttidiviyakuṁ be 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ṭṭina Uttamagaṁḍamāḍa 6 vī 
<lb n="9" break="no"/>niṁ jēkoni rā<unclear>vu</unclear>bōyuni ko 
<lb n="10" break="no"/>ḍuku dēvaya tana putrānupautri 
<lb n="11" break="no"/>kamu nityapaḍi naṁdimānika mā 
<lb n="12" break="no"/>neṁḍu nēyi vōsi yācaṁdrārkka 
<lb n="13" break="no"/>mu naḍapaṁggalavāṁḍu 
<lb n="14"/>Idi kolinā<unclear>cā</unclear>ryyalikitaṁ 
</p>

